18#ifndef OPENSSL_NO_CAST
19# include <openssl/cast.h>

21static unsigned char k[16] = {
22 0x01, 0x23, 0x45, 0x67, 0x12, 0x34, 0x56, 0x78,
23 0x23, 0x45, 0x67, 0x89, 0x34, 0x56, 0x78, 0x9A
24};
25
26static unsigned char in[8] =
27 { 0x01, 0x23, 0x45, 0x67, 0x89, 0xAB, 0xCD, 0xEF };
28
29static int k_len[3] = { 16, 10, 5 };
30
31static unsigned char c[3][8] = {
32 {0x23, 0x8B, 0x4F, 0xE5, 0x84, 0x7E, 0x44, 0xB2},
33 {0xEB, 0x6A, 0x71, 0x1A, 0x2C, 0x02, 0x27, 0x1B},
34 {0x7A, 0xC8, 0x16, 0xD1, 0x6E, 0x9B, 0x30, 0x2E},
35};
36
37static unsigned char in_a[16] = {
38 0x01, 0x23, 0x45, 0x67, 0x12, 0x34, 0x56, 0x78,
39 0x23, 0x45, 0x67, 0x89, 0x34, 0x56, 0x78, 0x9A
40};
41
42static unsigned char in_b[16] = {
43 0x01, 0x23, 0x45, 0x67, 0x12, 0x34, 0x56, 0x78,
44 0x23, 0x45, 0x67, 0x89, 0x34, 0x56, 0x78, 0x9A
45};
46
47static unsigned char c_a[16] = {
48 0xEE, 0xA9, 0xD0, 0xA2, 0x49, 0xFD, 0x3B, 0xA6,
49 0xB3, 0x43, 0x6F, 0xB8, 0x9D, 0x6D, 0xCA, 0x92
50};
51
52static unsigned char c_b[16] = {
53 0xB2, 0xC9, 0x5E, 0xB0, 0x0C, 0x31, 0xAD, 0x71,
54 0x80, 0xAC, 0x05, 0xB8, 0xE8, 0x3D, 0x69, 0x6E
55};
56
57static int cast_test_vector(int z)
58{
59 int testresult = 1;
60 CAST_KEY key;
61 unsigned char out[80];
62
63 CAST_set_key(&key, k_len[z], k);
64 CAST_ecb_encrypt(in, out, &key, CAST_ENCRYPT);
65 if (!TEST_mem_eq(out, sizeof(c[z]), c[z], sizeof(c[z]))) {
66 TEST_info("CAST_ENCRYPT iteration %d failed (len=%d)", z, k_len[z]);
67 testresult = 0;
68 }
69
70 CAST_ecb_encrypt(out, out, &key, CAST_DECRYPT);
71 if (!TEST_mem_eq(out, sizeof(in), in, sizeof(in))) {
72 TEST_info("CAST_DECRYPT iteration %d failed (len=%d)", z, k_len[z]);
73 testresult = 0;
74 }
75 return testresult;
76}
77
78static int cast_test_iterations(void)
79{
80 long l;
81 int testresult = 1;
82 CAST_KEY key, key_b;
83 unsigned char out_a[16], out_b[16];
84
85 memcpy(out_a, in_a, sizeof(in_a));
86 memcpy(out_b, in_b, sizeof(in_b));
87
88 for (l = 0; l < 1000000L; l++) {
89 CAST_set_key(&key_b, 16, out_b);
90 CAST_ecb_encrypt(&(out_a[0]), &(out_a[0]), &key_b, CAST_ENCRYPT);
91 CAST_ecb_encrypt(&(out_a[8]), &(out_a[8]), &key_b, CAST_ENCRYPT);
92 CAST_set_key(&key, 16, out_a);
93 CAST_ecb_encrypt(&(out_b[0]), &(out_b[0]), &key, CAST_ENCRYPT);
94 CAST_ecb_encrypt(&(out_b[8]), &(out_b[8]), &key, CAST_ENCRYPT);
95 }
96
97 if (!TEST_mem_eq(out_a, sizeof(c_a), c_a, sizeof(c_a))
98 || !TEST_mem_eq(out_b, sizeof(c_b), c_b, sizeof(c_b)))
99 testresult = 0;
100
101 return testresult;
102}
103#endif
104
105int setup_tests(void)
106{
107#ifndef OPENSSL_NO_CAST
108 ADD_ALL_TESTS(cast_test_vector, OSSL_NELEM(k_len));
109 ADD_TEST(cast_test_iterations);
110#endif
111 return 1;
112}
